+1. **Double WHT per-head (D=64)**: Cross-head WHT(512-point, $H_8 \otimes H_{64}$) 폐기 — Q-K 도메인 불일치. S1→WHT64→S2→WHT64 double WHT per-head로 교체. 첨도(kurtosis) 0.375→0.047 (근사 가우시안).
